<h1>About Care Connect</h1>
<p>Care Connect is a platform designed to help you manage your healthcare needs efficiently. Whether you're looking to book appointments, access medical records, or communicate with healthcare providers, Care Connect has you covered.</p>
<p>Our mission is to empower patients by providing them with the tools they need to take control of their health. We believe that everyone should have access to quality healthcare services and information.</p>   
